    <string name="about_title">About app</string>
    <string name="about_version">Version 1.0.0</string>
    <string name="about_description"><![CDATA[
<p><b>Eliza</b> is your personal oasis of calm. I was created to gently care for your mood and health. ✨</p>

<p><b>What we will do together:</b></p>
• <b>Feelings Diary:</b> write down your thoughts and store important moments with photos.<br>
• <b>Mood Lamp:</b> share events, and I will tell you the “color” of your day.<br>
• <b>Calendar:</b> I will help you track your cycle and predict important dates.<br>
• <b>Encouragements:</b> warm words from those who understand you.<br>
• <b>Chat with me:</b> I am always here to chat, find a recipe, or just listen. 🌸<br><br>

<i>All your secrets remain only on this device.</i><br><br>

<i><font color="#F06292">⚠️ This app is not a contraceptive and should not be used for pregnancy planning or prevention. If you experience any cycle irregularities, consult a doctor.</font></i><br><br>

Made with love for you. ❤️
]]></string>
